    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-806a-8311-f537a2e7b786",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Poor selection of undergraduate program leads to demotivation and greater dropout. To help Highschool graduates, the authors propose a career-path recommender system (PCRS), a recommender based on Fuzzy Intelligence from academic performance, personality type and extra-curricular skills. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-806a-8311-f537a2e7b786",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
